				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-giang-ph%C3%BA/poem-vkX_Mo8oekmvcSW48K_TFg">Bạch Đằng giang phú - 白藤江賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-s%C6%A1n-v%C5%A9/poem-mwfxESqrpLkmyCjRMF0Jwg">Đắc sơn vũ - 得山雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Phanh/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch-Lang-Quan-h%E1%BB%93/poem-NBgSj2r2KMNrTy5hVHHQUQ">Đề Lý Bạch Lang Quan hồ - 題李白郎官湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Phanh/author-KzYYRRdpC3C-h8YlLpfBMA">Phạm Phanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-ch%C3%AD-ca/poem--A3qpFL2UYH8DOEkrBgXVg">Đồ chí ca - 圖誌歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-ki%E1%BB%87u-xu%E1%BA%A5t-ch%C6%B0-s%C6%A1n-chi-%C4%91%E1%BB%89nh/poem-wgFiL4FhvuYKa8ECYf_bZQ">Độ Tuyền kiệu xuất chư sơn chi đỉnh - 渡泉嶠出諸山之頂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/author-BvX7SZcYDh6BIaZimIwj-Q">Giang Yêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-s%C6%A1n-trung/poem-02k1OtnlJyY4eLEMJFN2JQ">Hạ nhật sơn trung - 夏日山中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Long-M%C3%B4n-c%C3%A1c/poem-lrXP6OeRDYdKuhraWusTRA">Long Môn các - 龍門閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%